acs_tracts <- get_acs(
  geography = "tract",
  state     = "PA",
  county    = "Philadelphia",
  variables = acs_vars,
  year      = 2023,
  survey    = "acs5",
  geometry  = TRUE,
  cache_table = TRUE,
  progress = FALSE
) %>%
  select(GEOID, variable, estimate, geometry) %>%
  st_transform(st_crs(geo_clean)) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = variable, values_from = estimate) %>%
  st_as_sf()
